        "created_at": "2025-07-01T12:07:50.011Z",
        "cooked": "<p>When typing a new message or reply with longer text messages the text entry window stays the same size.  It would be helpful if this window would increase in size for longer text messages. On iOS when you use Messages and have a long message the entry window expands and allows you to see more text.</p>\n<p>This should also be the same behavior if you pasted in a longer text message. It makes it easier to scroll and review what is entered.</p>",
