        "cooked": "<p>Very closely related to this request which already has suggestions for dynamic expansion:</p><aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"6065\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/r/f0a364/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/more-space-when-creating-a-new-message/6065\">More space when creating a new message</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Could we have an option to set the number of lines for new messages.  4 lines is just not enough to read/check a long message. \nThanks.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
